// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// FLOW BISNIS
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//
// INBOUND:  suppliers → cycles → cycle_items → stocks (qty++)
// OUTBOUND: shoppings → shopping_items → stocks (qty-- validated)
//
// LIFECYCLE:
//   Cycle:    draft → receiving → completed
//   Shopping: draft → shipped → completed
//
// DELETE RULES:
//   CASCADE:  supplier_addresses, cycle_items, shopping_items
//   RESTRICT: products, cycles (supplier_id), stocks
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
